Element Parameter:

e:nphases               Phases

e:cpOwner               Owner   
e:cpOperator            Operator        
e:cpBranch              Branch  
e:cpSubstat             Substation      
e:cpSite                Site    
e:cpMeteostat           Meteo Station   
e:cpHeadFold            Head Folder     
e:fold_id               In Folder

e:ciEnergized           Energized       
e:ciEarthed             Earthed 
e:cDisplayName          Display Name

Load Flow AC balanced:
---------------------

Currents, Voltages and Powers:

m:u1r:bus1               p.u.   Positive-Sequence-Voltage, Real Part    
m:u1r:bus2               p.u.   Positive-Sequence-Voltage, Real Part    
m:u1i:bus1               p.u.   Positive-Sequence-Voltage, Imaginary Part

m:phii:bus2              deg    Current, Angle

m:I1:bus2                kA     Positive-Sequence Current, Magnitude

m:Spu:bus2               MVA/p.u.       Apparent Power per p.u. Voltage
